### Hadith 1:170

*Narrated Anas bin Malik:*

saw Allah's Apostle when the 'Asr prayer was due and the people searched
for water to perform ablution but they could not find it. Later on (a
pot full of) water for ablution was brought to Allah's Apostle . He put
his hand in that pot and ordered the people to perform ablution from it.
I saw the water springing out from underneath his fingers till all of
them performed the ablution (it was one of the miracles of the Prophet).

